@AmineYagoube created CodeTribunal to help teams audit freelance code more effectively.

It sets up an "AI Courtroom" where GLM-5.1 agents debate as prosecutor and defense to uncover hidden logical risks that standard linters might miss.
https://t.co/Bo17XGYYhD https://t.co/RLqh1l0uQ4

@Neelkamalshah built Builddy to go from a text prompt to a deployed web app in one go using GLM-5.1.

The system coordinates 6 different agents to handle everything from system design to final deployment, all running on GLM-5.1's coding logic.
https://t.co/j2cus3bla8 https://t.co/QoCRNx5Ogj
